# Design System

Aesthetic: a black archival music space illuminated by live stage color.
Target balance ~70% black/charcoal/ivory, 20% emerald/brass, 10% orange/magenta/violet.

## Tokens (never hard-code hex/px)
Use CSS variables / the token object from `src/client/design/tokens`.
Palette: bg `#080A09`, surface `#171A18`, raised `#242825`, text `#F1E9DA`,
secondary text `#B7B0A2`, emerald `#078A70` (primary interactive/CTA),
brass `#C49A47` (featured/archival), orange `#C64C27` (high-energy),
magenta `#8C4F78`, violet `#554B69` (sparingly). Radii 4-8px, minimal shadows.

## Typography
Display: Cormorant Garamond. Body/UI: Manrope. Metadata/dates/setlists: IBM Plex Mono.
Brand wordmark: Bodoni Moda.

## Breakpoints
Documented in `tokens.css`: sm 480, md 768, lg 1024, xl 1280. Applied inline in CSS modules — no Tailwind, no shared mixin.
- **md boundary:** mobile rules use `@media (max-width: 767px)`; desktop rules use `min-width: 768px`.
- Prefer CSS `@media` for show/hide/layout. Use `useMediaQuery` only when JS must branch (e.g. tab routing).

## Mobile (≤767px)
Browse + add memories only on event detail. Implemented via CSS hides + `useMediaQuery` in `EventDetailView` / `EventPosterCard`.

| Area | Behavior |
|------|----------|
| Nav | Admin link hidden (`hideOnMobile` on nav item + `.hideOnMobile` in `shell.module.css`) |
| Timeline | Year pills, vertical line, markers, track padding hidden (`Timeline.module.css`) |
| Event detail | Tab bar hidden; `effectiveTab` forced to `summary`; hero tags stack; media gallery horizontal scroll-snap carousel |
| Event detail edits | Sidebar edit buttons, poster card, memory edit/delete, media upload hidden |
| Event detail writes | Only "Add membery" (`MemoriesSection`) remains |

Sidebar acts/setlist/personnel stay visible read-only. Poster card hidden entirely on mobile (`.eventPosterCard`).

## Accessibility (hard requirements)
- No text below the design-system minimum body size; no small/low-contrast copy.
- Icons supplement labels, never replace meaningful text; keep accessible labels.
- Important actions must be visible without hover.
- Sidebars reflow into content flow on mobile - never horizontally compressed.
- Memories render as liner-note annotations with a thin brass rule, not chat bubbles.

## Shared components & CSS
- **Cards:** `PerformanceCard` (grid cards), `TimelineEventCard` (timeline rows).
  Both use `MediaAvailabilityIndicators` for media badges — do not duplicate icon logic.
- **Filter bars:** `filterBar`, `filterBarDropdowns`, `filterBarInline` in
  `components/layout/layout.module.css` — not per-route `.filters` blocks.
- **Editor modals:** form layout in `components/form/modal.module.css`
  (`.modalForm`, `.modalActions`, `.modalList`, `.modalError`).
- **Event sidebar:** card chrome in `components/event/event.module.css`.
- Form controls accept an `error` prop — use it for client-side Zod validation feedback.
